    "description": "《Etnia（伊特尼亚）》是一款复古风格ARPG，至多支持一人游玩，你将会扮演一名少年，为了追寻梦想而开启一段充满坎坷的冒险。<br>你会在伊特尼亚大陆上经历丰富多彩的故事剧情；收集藏在遗迹、洞穴中的宝物；挑战形态各异的BOSS。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点：</h2><br><strong>• 超150件独特装备：</strong><br>每件装备都拥有它独特的效果，收集并且搭配它们，打造属于你的独特战斗方式。<br>比如：【游侠的把戏】  +  【自然之怒】<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209320/extras/df6ffa6c4764afad3c6bac3c39deb1f2.avif?t=1769418553\" width=278 height=380 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209320/extras/1cbe03abbb01826b8d0819e7bebdfe3d.avif?t=1769418553\" width=280 height=354 /></span><br>现在！你只需要将草丛，布满怪物的四周，随后…一触即发！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209320/extras/f77af6240f40c9275cee8b666f32983d.poster.avif?t=1769418553\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209320/extras/f77af6240f40c9275cee8b666f32983d.webm?t=1769418553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209320/extras/f77af6240f40c9275cee8b666f32983d.mp4?t=1769418553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>· 超15种主动技能：</strong><br>熟练掌握它们，在战斗中不断压制敌人！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209320/extras/8fcc003f96c9fe8be173a29003387d5c.poster.avif?t=1769418553\" width=600 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209320/extras/8fcc003f96c9fe8be173a29003387d5c.webm?t=1769418553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209320/extras/8fcc003f96c9fe8be173a29003387d5c.mp4?t=1769418553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209320/extras/a86e832e32e7f6887d5575954433cc31.poster.avif?t=1769418553\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209320/extras/a86e832e32e7f6887d5575954433cc31.webm?t=1769418553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209320/extras/a86e832e32e7f6887d5575954433cc31.mp4?t=1769418553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209320/extras/67c808a2318b64315266af858bdb3660.poster.avif?t=1769418553\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209320/extras/67c808a2318b64315266af858bdb3660.webm?t=1769418553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209320/extras/67c808a2318b64315266af858bdb3660.mp4?t=1769418553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>· 不同种族的NPC</strong><br>伊特尼亚大陆上许多形态各异的族群，与他们相识，了解他们的故事！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209320/extras/40506b0965ae1a49e0bc41633250ca2b.apng?t=1769418553\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209320/extras/40506b0965ae1a49e0bc41633250ca2b.poster.avif?t=1769418553\" class=\"bb_img\" width=144 height=144 /></picture></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209320/extras/0d85f4415d3a17c4295e31d8f3a3aa0e.apng?t=1769418553\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.c